Suppliers of Heavy Equipment Spare parts,Trailer Parts

We are specialized suppliers of genuine and OEM Heavy Earth Moving Equipment parts and truck spare parts for IVECO, MAN, MERCEDES ACTROS, RENAULT, VOLVO, SCANIA and supply of Trailer parts for ROR, YORK, BPW, SAF,FUWA and BOSCH vehicles in UAE.

Our Products ranges from spare parts such as Axle, Chassis And Trailer Body,Workshop Consumables And Tools for Workshops,different types of  Braking spares for different vehicles, Electrical And Lighting parts, Engine parts,Cabin and accessories, suspensions and its parts,Transmission parts, and equipment for Fuel ,Exhaust and after treatments
